-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------                INSTALL - XtraUpload v.3.0.0               -----------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  It is very simple to install.

  1. If you can use mod_rewrite, edit RewriteBase into .htaccess.
     ex: RewriteBase /xtraupload-v3

     If you cannot use mod_rewrite, edit $config['index_page'] = 'index.php'; in application/config/config.php.template.

  2. Just put the Web server simply.
     ex: /var/www/html/xtraupload-v3

  3. Go to your web site!
     ex: http://yoursite.ltd/xtraupload-v3/
